Adult.description: Say's Phoebes have a cinnamon wash on the flanks and tail similar to Vermilion Flycatchers, but they lack the whitish, streaked chest of female Vermilion Flycatchers.

Breeding male.description: Breeding male Scarlet Tanagers are larger with a thicker bill than Vermilion Flycatchers. They also have red backs whereas adult male Vermilions have a black back.
